Comment.val: /*Program that assembles the SingleOrderCreate xml message to be send to Fintegrator. */

Text.val: Virtuals to write the XML Message
Record for SingleOrderNew not found --> Error
executingFirm --> Optional, but when provided: id --> Manditory
clientID --> Optional, but when provided: id --> Manditory
clearingFirm --> Optional, but when provided: id --> Manditory
clearingAccount --> Optional, but when provided: id --> Manditory
investorID --> Optional, but when provided: id --> Manditory
enteringFirm --> Optional, but when provided: id --> Manditory
settlementLocation --> Optional, but when provided: id --> Manditory
originationTrader --> Optional, but when provided: id --> Manditory
originationFirm --> Optional, but when provided: id --> Manditory, dataSourceScheme --> Optional
securityID --> Optional, but when provided: id --> Manditory, sourceID --> Manditory
securityAltID --> Optional, but when provided: id --> Manditory, sourceID --> Manditory
putOrCall --> Optional (value 0 is a valid value, so no check on putOrCall <> 0)
underlyingID --> Optional, but when provided: id --> Manditory, sourceID --> Manditory
orderQtyData --> Manditory, orderQty --> Manditory OR cashOrderQty --> Manditory
clientType --> Optional (NB in EP+ is this the column RelationKind)
